My toy shop Laravel 10 + Vue 3 project


You need to make sure already install php,composer,apache (Xampp) or anyother and nodejs and vue3 in your computer.

admin site with laravel
    
-to serve project
 1.add new db table in php_my_admin 
 2.declare php_my_admin table name in DB_DATABASE = tablename
 3.php artisan migrate:fresh --seed
 4.php artisan serve

login admin pannel(email : admin@gmail.com) (password : admin123)
 
if doesn't work correctly
1.php artisan config:cache
2.php artisan config:clear
3.php artisan cache:clear 

4.delete vendor folder and open terminal 
type (composer install) if linux os (use sudo composer install)
do these following steps
 1.add new db table in php_my_admin 
 2.declare php_my_admin table name in DB_DATABASE = tablename
 3.php artisan migrate:fresh --seed
 4.php artisan serve

//______________________________________________________


to serve client-site (VUE3)
I used these packages
    "axios": "^1.5.0",
    "bootstrap": "^5.3.1",
    "vue-loading-overlay": "^6.0.3",
    "vue-router": "^4.0.3",
    "vue-star-rating": "^2.1.0",
    "vuejs-paginate-next": "^1.0.2",
    "vuex": "^4.0.0"

1.npm run serve

if doesn't work correctly

delete node_modules and run these command in terminal
(npm install) if linux os (use sudo npm install)
then serve project
npm run serve

